IVX LANDING PAGE — FINAL END-TO-END QA, FIX, DEPLOY, AND LIVE CERTIFICATION

CURRENT STATUS

The current report proves:

- landing route returns HTTP 200;
- /auth and related routes return 200;
- expected content strings exist in the live bundle;
- IVX colors are present;
- selected APIs return 200;
- TypeScript has zero errors.

This is not sufficient for final certification.

Do not repeat bundle-string checks as the primary proof.
Do not mark production ready because routes return 200.
Do not mark signup complete without creating and verifying a real account.
Do not mark media complete without real playback and interaction.
Do not return narrative only.

Execute the complete landing-page QA, fix every defect, redeploy, retest, and return evidence.

==================================================
1. CANONICAL DOMAIN AND ROUTE QA
==================================================

Audit:

https://ivxholding.com/
https://www.ivxholding.com/
https://chat.ivxholding.com/
https://chat.ivxholding.com/auth
https://ivxholding.com/auth
https://ivxholding.com/login
https://ivxholding.com/signup
https://ivxholding.com/member-register
https://ivxholding.com/legal

Verify:

- one canonical landing domain;
- HTTPS only;
- no redirect loops;
- no duplicate landing versions;
- old login/signup routes redirect correctly;
- no stale bundle;
- no mixed content;
- no 404;
- no blank page.

Return:

ROUTE
HTTP_STATUS
FINAL_URL
REDIRECT_CHAIN
BUILD_SHA
STATUS

==================================================
2. LIVE VISUAL QA
==================================================

Test the real production page on:

- Android Chrome
- iPhone Safari
- desktop Chrome
- desktop Safari
- tablet
- small mobile width
- large desktop width

Verify:

- hero renders correctly;
- IVX logo is sharp;
- headline is readable;
- buttons fit;
- no horizontal overflow;
- no clipped text;
- no overlapping cards;
- no white banner;
- no layout jump;
- no image distortion;
- no text cut-off;
- bottom navigation does not appear incorrectly on public web;
- safe-area spacing works;
- card heights are consistent;
- dark theme remains consistent;
- yellow/green accents are used intentionally.

Provide screenshots for each viewport.

==================================================
3. LANDING PAGE JUMP AND STABILITY AUDIT
==================================================

Audit every cause of jumping:

- image dimensions not reserved;
- video dimensions not reserved;
- font swap;
- late API content;
- carousel remeasurement;
- autoplay video;
- lazy loading;
- conditional banners;
- dynamic member counts;
- horizontal sliders;
- hydration mismatch;
- CSS transitions;
- scroll restoration;
- sticky headers;
- mobile keyboard;
- route transitions;
- image decode delay;
- video metadata delay;
- ads or embeds;
- analytics injection;
- animated counters.

Measure:

CLS
LCP
INP
FCP
TTFB

Required:

- no visible jump when loading;
- no post cards changing height unexpectedly;
- no slider snapping to a different position;
- no content moving when images/videos load;
- no duplicate render after hydration.

Return exact root cause and fix for every shift.

==================================================
4. HERO AND PRIMARY CTA QA
==================================================

Verify all primary actions:

- Explore
- Browse Properties
- View JV Deals
- Buy Now
- Details
- Invest Now
- Get Started
- Sign Up
- Login

For every button return:

BUTTON
SOURCE_ROUTE
DESTINATION
HTTP_STATUS
SCREEN_RENDERED
AUTH_REQUIRED
ERROR
STATUS

No dead button.
No placeholder route.
No route ending in a generic screen.

==================================================
5. PROPERTY AND DEAL QA
==================================================

Verify all visible live deals and featured properties.

For every card test:

- title;
- image;
- investment amount;
- ROI;
- location;
- fractional amount;
- ownership minimum;
- badges;
- developer name;
- Details;
- Invest Now;
- Buy Now;
- image carousel;
- deal status.

Check:

- no duplicated properties;
- no stale prices;
- no incorrect deal/video association;
- no broken images;
- no false “LIVE” or “VERIFIED” badge;
- no card overflow;
- all data matches production database.

Return UI/API/database comparison.

==================================================
6. MEDIA AND REELS QA
==================================================

Verify:

- images load;
- videos play;
- thumbnails load;
- autoplay behavior is correct;
- mute/unmute works;
- pause/resume works;
- swipe works;
- no jump between posts;
- likes work;
- comments work;
- shares work;
- save works;
- loading state works;
- error state works;
- retry works;
- mobile data mode works;
- slow network works.

Verify intended order:

3 property/deal posts
→ 1 video
→ repeat

Return:

TOTAL_POSTS
TOTAL_DEALS
TOTAL_VIDEOS
ORDER_VALID
UNMATCHED_VIDEOS
BROKEN_MEDIA
STATUS

==================================================
7. REGISTRATION ENTRY QA
==================================================

Verify that landing-page registration opens the new IVX auth experience.

Test:

- Get Started;
- Sign Up;
- Investor Portal signup link;
- member registration link;
- auth tab selection;
- back button;
- close button;
- deep link to signup mode.

Required:

- no duplicate signup screen;
- no old registration popup;
- no conflicting auth flow;
- one canonical auth route;
- no auto-login;
- correct manual login behavior.

==================================================
8. REAL MEMBER SIGNUP E2E
==================================================

Create one production-safe QA member through the live landing page.

Verify:

1. first name;
2. last name;
3. email;
4. phone;
5. password;
6. role;
7. optional photo;
8. terms;
9. email verification;
10. phone verification if active;
11. auth user created;
12. profile created;
13. member row created;
14. role saved;
15. source marked as landing;
16. correct dashboard opens;
17. member appears in Admin HQ;
18. member count updates;
19. no duplicate row;
20. logout/login works.

Return:

AUTH_USER_ID
PROFILE_ID
MEMBER_ID
ROLE
SOURCE
EMAIL_VERIFIED
PHONE_VERIFIED
ADMIN_VISIBLE
COUNT_UPDATED
STATUS

Deactivate or remove only the QA account after evidence is preserved.

==================================================
9. LOGIN QA
==================================================

Test:

- valid member;
- valid investor;
- valid owner;
- invalid email;
- wrong password;
- suspended user;
- unverified email;
- logout;
- forgot password;
- remember me OFF by default;
- no owner auto-login.

Verify the owner cannot be created from public registration.

==================================================
10. ANALYTICS AND CONVERSION QA
==================================================

Verify tracking for:

- page view;
- unique visitor;
- property impression;
- video view;
- CTA click;
- signup start;
- signup completion;
- login;
- property details;
- invest click;
- share;
- lead submission.

Check:

- events are not duplicated;
- anonymous session converts to authenticated user;
- campaign/UTM attribution persists;
- owner analytics sees the event;
- timestamps use UTC storage and viewer time zone display;
- no PII is leaked into public analytics.

Return the event IDs for one complete test journey.

==================================================
11. SEO QA
==================================================

Verify:

- title;
- meta description;
- canonical URL;
- Open Graph;
- X/Twitter cards;
- favicon;
- robots.txt;
- sitemap.xml;
- structured data;
- property/deal metadata;
- social preview image;
- mobile viewport.

Check the page with JavaScript disabled enough to confirm meaningful metadata exists.

==================================================
12. ACCESSIBILITY QA
==================================================

Verify:

- semantic headings;
- one H1;
- button labels;
- form labels;
- alt text;
- keyboard navigation;
- focus order;
- focus visibility;
- screen reader names;
- color contrast;
- reduced motion;
- touch-target size;
- error announcement;
- modal focus trap;
- Escape/close behavior;
- no color-only meaning.

Return automated and manual accessibility results.

==================================================
13. PERFORMANCE QA
==================================================

Measure on mobile and desktop:

TTFB
FCP
LCP
CLS
INP
TOTAL_JS
TOTAL_CSS
TOTAL_IMAGE_BYTES
TOTAL_VIDEO_BYTES
REQUEST_COUNT

Investigate the reported 13.2 MB bundle.

Required actions:

- identify largest modules;
- identify accidental imports;
- code-split admin-only code;
- lazy-load noncritical sections;
- optimize images;
- defer videos;
- remove duplicate libraries;
- ensure public landing does not load Owner/Admin modules.

Return before/after measurements.

==================================================
14. SECURITY QA
==================================================

Verify:

- no secrets in client bundle;
- no service-role key;
- no GitHub/Render/AWS/AI keys;
- CSP configured;
- CORS correct;
- secure cookies;
- anti-CSRF where required;
- login/signup rate limiting;
- bot protection;
- MIME validation;
- file-size validation;
- open redirect blocked;
- XSS inputs sanitized;
- SQL/API injection blocked;
- owner routes protected;
- unauthorized API calls return 401/403;
- public routes expose only public data.

==================================================
15. ERROR AND OFFLINE QA
==================================================

Test:

- API unavailable;
- slow API;
- image unavailable;
- video unavailable;
- auth unavailable;
- Supabase unavailable;
- network offline;
- network restored;
- timeout;
- 401;
- 403;
- 404;
- 500.

The page must:

- remain usable where possible;
- show honest errors;
- show retry;
- not display fake data;
- not crash;
- not lose form input unnecessarily;
- preserve completed signup when safe.

==================================================
16. BROWSER CONSOLE AND NETWORK QA
==================================================

On all target browsers verify:

CONSOLE_ERRORS=0
UNHANDLED_REJECTIONS=0
FAILED_NETWORK_REQUESTS=0
MIXED_CONTENT=0
HYDRATION_ERRORS=0
CORS_ERRORS=0
DEPRECATED_API_WARNINGS=0

List every remaining warning separately.

==================================================
17. CACHE AND DEPLOYMENT QA
==================================================

Verify:

- latest GitHub SHA;
- latest frontend build SHA;
- backend SHA;
- cache headers;
- CDN invalidation;
- service worker behavior;
- hard refresh;
- private/incognito load;
- repeat visit;
- stale bundle prevention.

Required equality:

GITHUB_HEAD_SHA
=
LIVE_FRONTEND_SHA
=
EXPECTED_LANDING_BUILD_SHA

Backend-dependent routes must match the deployed backend version.

==================================================
18. OWNER CONTROL QA
==================================================

Verify the owner can manage landing content:

- hero text;
- CTA labels;
- property order;
- featured properties;
- videos;
- banners;
- registration state;
- legal links;
- analytics;
- submissions.

Test one safe content update:

1. owner edits;
2. saves;
3. audit event created;
4. production reflects update;
5. rollback restores previous value.

==================================================
19. FINAL FIX AND REGRESSION PASS
==================================================

Fix every critical and medium issue found.

Then rerun:

- routes;
- signup;
- login;
- properties;
- media;
- analytics;
- accessibility;
- performance;
- security;
- mobile visual QA;
- desktop visual QA;
- cache/deployment chain.

==================================================
20. FINAL EVIDENCE PACKAGE
==================================================

Return:

CANONICAL_URL=
GITHUB_SHA=
FRONTEND_BUILD_SHA=
BACKEND_SHA=
DEPLOY_TIME=
CACHE_STATUS=

ROUTES_TOTAL=
ROUTES_PASS=
BUTTONS_TOTAL=
BUTTONS_PASS=

PROPERTIES_TESTED=
VIDEOS_TESTED=
MEDIA_ERRORS=

SIGNUP_PASS=
LOGIN_PASS=
OWNER_LOGIN_PASS=
MEMBER_SYNC_PASS=

ANALYTICS_PASS=
SEO_PASS=
ACCESSIBILITY_PASS=
SECURITY_PASS=
PERFORMANCE_PASS=
OFFLINE_PASS=

ANDROID_PASS=
IOS_PASS=
DESKTOP_PASS=
TABLET_PASS=

CLS=
LCP=
INP=
FCP=
TTFB=
TOTAL_BUNDLE_SIZE=

OPEN_CRITICAL_BUGS=
OPEN_MEDIUM_BUGS=
OPEN_LOW_BUGS=

==================================================
FINAL VERDICT
==================================================

Return exactly one:

IVX LANDING PAGE VERIFIED LIVE END TO END

or

IVX LANDING PAGE NOT CERTIFIED

Do not return VERIFIED unless:

- real visual QA passes;
- no jumping remains;
- every CTA works;
- all property/deal cards are correct;
- media ordering and playback work;
- a real signup completes;
- member data reaches Admin HQ;
- login and recovery work;
- analytics events are verified;
- accessibility passes;
- security passes;
- mobile and desktop pass;
- GitHub SHA matches the live build;
- no critical or medium bugs remain.

If incomplete, return only:

FAILED_SECTION:
PLATFORM:
ROUTE:
ERROR:
ROOT_CAUSE:
FILE:
FUNCTION:
